headline: State Street Global Advisors’ 2025 Global Market Outlook: Finding the Right Path
summary: BOSTON, December 04, 2024--State Street Global Advisors, the asset management business of State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT), today launched its 2025 Global Market Outlook: Finding the Right Path, outlining its macroeconomic outlook and key investment themes for the year ahead.
